Homepage: https://localhost/tiengviet
Description: Tiếng Việt - Vietnamese learning app for Russian speakers
 Tiếng Việt is a Vietnamese language learning application for Russian
 speakers. It includes lessons, flashcards, writing practice, search,
 autoplay and local text-to-speech features.
